title: [Gyldemar Forest, Stairwell]
description: A wide crack travels the length of the stairwell while light from grates set into the walls above cuts through the gloom.  The musty smell of decaying plant matter makes the air heavy and unpleasant.

A wide crack travels the length of the stairwell while a small amount of light from the night sky filters through the grates set into the walls above.  The musty smell of decaying plant matter makes the air heavy and unpleasant.
